Recorded Points

How to Use This Tool

  1. Click anywhere on the skeleton image to place a marker
  2. Fill in the form with Title, Name, and Description
  3. Drag points to adjust their positions
  4. Drag labels to adjust their positions and avoid overlapping
  5. Click on points to select them, then use Connect Points to draw lines between selected points
  6. Use Import JSON to load existing point data
  7. Click on point labels or coordinate items to view detailed information
  8. Use Copy Selected to copy selected points to clipboard
  9. Use Paste Points to add points from clipboard
  10. Use the Export Data button to save all coordinates
  11. Use the Clear All button to remove all points and lines
